    <!-- Welcome / First Launch -->
    <string name="welcome_title">Murakaza neza</string>
    <string name="welcome_sovereignty">Infunguzo zawe.\nAmafaranga yawe.\nUbwigenge bwawe.</string>
    <string name="welcome_desc">Amafaranga yawe NTABIKWA muri iyi porogaramu. Abaho kuri blockchain, ayoborwa n\'infunguzo zawe z\'ibanga.\n\nIyi porogaramu ibika gusa infunguzo zawe neza. Ntidushobora kubona amafaranga yawe.\n\nIcyitonderwa: Token zimwe (USDC, USDT) zishobora gufungwa n\'abazitanga. Kugira ngo ubone ubwigenge bwuzuye, koresha ETH y\'umwimerere cyangwa token zigenga.</string>
    <string name="welcome_warning_title">Infunguzo zawe = Amafaranga yawe</string>
    <string name="welcome_warning_desc">Niba wabura infunguzo zawe z\'ibanga cyangwa ukazisangiza n\'undi muntu, ubura ubuyobozi ku mafaranga yawe burundu.\n\nNta buryo bwo kugarura. Nta muryango w\'ubufasha ushobora kugufasha. Ibi ni kamere y\'ubunyagathane nyakuri.\n\nBuri gihe bika kopi y\'umutekano y\'infunguzo zawe.</string>
    <string name="welcome_opensource">Porogaramu ifunguye. Genzura, ntukizere.</string>
    <string name="welcome_start">Narabyumvise, reka dutangire</string>

